longBusinessSummary: Shonghoya Intl Group Inc., a development stage company, focuses on operating as an Internet-based social media company. It intends to market coupons to local merchants for the daily deals in tier 2 markets. The company was formerly known as Deal A Day Group Corp. and changed its name to Shonghoya Intl Group Inc. in June 2020. Shonghoya Intl Group Inc. is based in New Taipei City, Taiwan.
